(TENDER FOR DESILTING OF VISVESVARAYA CANAL   MYSURU REACH \(PACKAGE DS-07\)) Tj T*
(Chainage: Km 96.400 to Km 110.700 \(14.3 km\)) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(================================================================================) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(1. WORK DETAILS) Tj T*
(================================================================================) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Cauvery Neeravari Nigam Limited \(CNNL\), Mysuru Irrigation Division, invites) Tj T*
(online tenders from eligible contractors for the following work:) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Work Name    : Desilting of Visvesvaraya Canal \(Mysuru Reach\), Package DS-07) Tj T*
(Location     : Chainage Km 96.400 to Km 110.700, Mysuru District, Karnataka) Tj T*
(Scope        : Mechanical and manual desilting of the main canal bed and banks,) Tj T*
(               disposal of silt, restoration of embankment slopes \(1:1.5\),) Tj T*
(               repair and re-plastering of CC lining \(grade M15\) at 23 locations,) Tj T*
(               reconstruction of 4 cross-drainage structures \(sluice type\),) Tj T*
(               vegetation clearance on canal banks \(both sides, 14.3 km\),) Tj T*
(               and desilting of 6 field channels \(each 0.8 1.4 km\).) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Estimated Cost   : Rs. 4,10,00,000/- \(Rs. Four Crore Ten Lakh\)) Tj T*
(EMD              : Rs. 82,000/- \(Rs. Eighty-Two Thousand\)   2% of estimated cost) Tj T*
(Tender Fee       : Rs. 2,000/- \(non-refundable, paid online\)) Tj T*
(Performance Security : 5% of accepted contract value) Tj T*
(Defect Liability Period : 12 months from date of substantial completion) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(================================================================================) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(2. IMPORTANT DATES) Tj T*
(================================================================================) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Publication of e-NIT          : 10 June 2026) Tj T*
(Last date for document download : 05 July 2026, 17:30 hrs) Tj T*
(Last date for clarifications  : 08 July 2026) Tj T*
(Pre-Bid Meeting               : 10 July 2026, 11:00 hrs at CNNL Mysuru Divisional Office) Tj T*
(Last date for bid submission  : 22 July 2026, 17:00 hrs) Tj T*
(Opening of Technical Bids     : 24 July 2026, 11:00 hrs) Tj T*
(Bid validity                  : 120 days from date of submission) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Bids must be submitted online on the Karnataka e-Procurement portal) Tj T*
(\(https://eproc.karnataka.gov.in\). Physical submission not accepted.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(================================================================================) Tj T*
() Tj T*
