(  The bidder shall have successfully completed at least 1 \(one\) similar canal) Tj T*
(  work or irrigation scheme work during the last 5 \(five\) years \(on or after) Tj T*
(  01 April 2021\), of value not less than Rs. 1.50 Crore.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(  "Similar work" means: Desilting, embankment repair, or canal lining work on) Tj T*
(  an irrigation canal, distributary, or field channel maintained by an) Tj T*
(  Irrigation Department, CNNL, KNNL, CADA, or equivalent organisation.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(  Works involving road embankments, building construction, or drainage of) Tj T*
(  non-irrigation structures shall NOT qualify as similar work for this purpose.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(  Supporting documents: Work order + Performance / Completion certificate from) Tj T*
(  the concerned Irrigation Department or parastatal, specifying the nature,) Tj T*
(  value, and date of completion of the work.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(4.3 Contractor Registration) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(  The bidder shall hold a valid registration as Class II Contractor or above) Tj T*
(  \(Class I, Special Class\) with:) Tj T*
(  \(a\) Karnataka Public Works Department \(KPWD\), OR) Tj T*
(  \(b\) Karnataka Rural Infrastructure Development Limited \(KRIDL\), OR) Tj T*
(  \(c\) CNNL / KNNL \(irrigation department registration\), OR) Tj T*
(  \(d\) Central Water Commission \(CWC\) / CPWD equivalent category) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(  A road-only PWD registration without an irrigation/hydraulic works endorsement) Tj T*
(  does not satisfy this condition.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(4.4 Other Documents Required) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(  \(a\) Valid GST Registration \(GSTIN\)) Tj T*
(  \(b\) PAN) Tj T*
(  \(c\) EPF / ESIC Registration) Tj T*
(  \(d\) Undertaking that no litigation / arbitration is pending with any) Tj T*
(      Irrigation Department in Karnataka) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(================================================================================) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(5. EVALUATION CRITERIA) Tj T*
(================================================================================) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(5.1 Technical bids will be evaluated on pass/fail basis against Section 4.) Tj T*
(    Only technically qualified bidders will proceed to financial bid opening.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(5.2 Financial bids will be evaluated on L1 \(lowest valid bid\) basis.) Tj T*
(    Bids above 10% of estimated cost shall not be considered for award.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(5.3 CNNL reserves the right to award work to L2 if L1 fails to execute) Tj T*
(    the agreement within 7 working days of letter of award.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(================================================================================) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(6. SITE CONDITIONS) Tj T*
(================================================================================) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(6.1 Canal water shall be shut down for the work season \(1 October to 31 March\).) Tj T*
